<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IFRS15_IE199" base="F31820445"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>IE199</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS&#xa0;15"/><data name="paranum" value="IE199"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P1442">The same facts as in Case&#xa0;A apply to Case&#xa0;B except that the contract is non-cancellable. The following journal entries illustrate how the entity accounts for the contract:</p><ol outputclass="static" id="IFRS15_L0124" base="F31820448" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS15_P1443" base="F31820449">The amount of consideration is due on 31&#xa0;January 20X9 (which is when the entity recognises a receivable because it has an unconditional right to consideration):</p> <table id="IFRS15_TAB0020" base="SL31820596" frame="none" orient="port"><tgroup cols="5"><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="3*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="47*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="3" colname="C3" colwidth="27*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="4" colname="C4" colwidth="3*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="5" colname="C5" colwidth="20*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><tbody><row keep_together="1"><entry namest="C1" nameend="C2" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1444" typeface="sansserif">Receivable</p></entry><entry colname="C3" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1445" typeface="sansserif">CU1,000</p></entry><entry colname="C4"> <p id="IFRS15_P1446" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C5"> <p id="IFRS15_P1447" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRS15_P1448" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1449" typeface="sansserif">Contract liability</p></entry><entry namest="C3" nameend="C4" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1450" typeface="sansserif">CU1,000</p></entry><entry colname="C5"> <p id="IFRS15_P1451" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS15_P1452" base="F31820451">The entity receives the cash on 1&#xa0;March 20X9:</p> <table id="IFRS15_TAB0021" base="SL31820604" frame="none" orient="port"><tgroup cols="5"><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="3*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="47*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="3" colname="C3" colwidth="27*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="4" colname="C4" colwidth="3*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="5" colname="C5" colwidth="20*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><tbody><row keep_together="1"><entry namest="C1" nameend="C2" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1453" typeface="sansserif">Cash</p></entry><entry colname="C3" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1454" typeface="sansserif">CU1,000</p></entry><entry colname="C4"> <p id="IFRS15_P1455" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C5"> <p id="IFRS15_P1456" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRS15_P1457" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1458" typeface="sansserif">Receivable</p></entry><entry namest="C3" nameend="C4" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P1459" typeface="sansserif">CU1,000</p></entry><entry colname="C5"> <p id="IFRS15_P1460" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS15_P1461" base="F31820453">The entity satisfies the performance obligation on 31&#xa0;March 20X9:</p> <table id="IFRS15_TAB0022" base="SL31820612" frame="none" orient="port"><tgroup cols="5"><colspec colnum="1"